		BeShare :
			- Available at http://www.bebits.com/app/1330
			
		JavaShare :
			- Basic BeShare client with no file sharing capabilities (yet). Should run on any java enabled OS.
			  Available at http://www.bebits.com/app/2795

		Ozone :
			- Basic BeShare client with file sharing capabilities. Runs on Windows, Linux and Mac.
			  Available at http://www.magep.com/ozone/index.php?page=download

		Unizone :
			- Excellent BeShare client. Supports unicode and nearly all BeShare features. Runs on Windows.
			  Available at http://www.raasu.org/tools/windows